	<div class="mb-6">
		<h1 class="pb-2 font-bold text-3xl text-gray-600">First iOS app released!</h1>
    
	</div>
  <div class="text-content">
    <p>Back in December I took the plunge to expand my skill set a bit more, I start on a <a href="https://www.udemy.com" target="_blank">Udemy</a> course for iOS development.</p>

<p>4 weeks later, I now have my first app on the App Store!</p>

<p>Ok so its nothing groundbreaking but it’s a start.</p>

<p><a href="https://apps.apple.com/gb/app/mono-weather/id1495912833" target="_blank">Mono Weather</a> is a minimalist weather app, that simply provides you with the weather for your current location.</p>

